## 6 — 30/60/90 plan

**Days 0–30 (foundation):** ship answer-first blocks on priority pages, add Product + FAQPage + BreadcrumbList schema, fix homepage LCP, refresh HIPAA page with dateModified.

**Days 31–60 (authority):** author bylines + Person schema across features and compliance, submit Wikidata QID, publish transcripts for all product-demo video, rewrite thin meta descriptions.

**Days 61–90 (measurement):** re-run the {{ rollups.prompt_count }}-prompt LLM panel, measure citation-share lift, A/B the new answer blocks, decide whether to expand to {{ intake.buyer_questions | length * 2 }} prompts next quarter.

